name: List Of Property Near Expiry
query:
select 
P.property_name AS Property, 
P.property_type AS "Property Type",
PT.rent_end_date AS "Expires On" ,
PT.rent_start_date AS "Rent Started On" ,
PT.rent_price AS "Rent Price",
PT.rent_duration AS "Rent Duration (Months)",
PT.customer AS "Client",
PT.telephone AS "Telephone",
PT.customer_email AS "Email",
PT.commission_from_client AS "Commission From Client:Currency",
PT.is_paid_by_client AS "Paid by Client",
P.customer AS "Property Owner",
P.telephone AS "Owner Contact",
P.email  AS "Owner Email",
PT.commission_from_owner AS "Commission From Owner:Currency",
PT.is_paid_by_owner AS "Paid by Owner"

from `tabProperty`AS P INNER JOIN
`tabProperty Transaction` AS PT 
ON PT.property = P.name 
where P.property_status = "Rented" 
and DATEDIFF (rent_end_date , CURDATE()) <= 60
and PT.docstatus = 1;
